With many looking to step up their skincare regime as they get older, Boots has a huge selection of brands and products, ranging from affordable to premium options. Boots has been running a £10 Tuesday weekly offer for a while, reducing a selection of skincare, makeup and beauty tools to £10 for one day only.   The capsules each contain the perfect amount of product, avoiding waste and ideal for travel as they are air-tight and protect the product from leakage.   Shoppers have started leaving reviews, with 89 percent of Boots shoppers saying they would recommend the product to a friend. 